OL,3,CSiege and slaughter: The border town
OL,4,Cwith a bloody role in British history
OL,6,FTom Barton looks at the role Berwick
OL,7,Fhas played in British history for
OL,9,FBerwick-Upon-Tweed is a small town
OL,10,Fwith a big history.
OL,12,FWith a strategic geographical position
OL,13,F- as the last town in England before
OL,14,Fthe Scottish Border - it has
OL,15,Ffrequently been fought over through
OL,16,Fthe centuries.
OL,18,FIn the 300 years from 1296, Berwick
OL,19,Fchanged hands between the Scottish and
OL,20,FEnglish 13 times.
