OL,3,CSiege and slaughter: The border town
OL,4,Cwith a bloody role in British history
OL,6,FJustin Gudgeon runs the Castle Vale
OL,7,FHouse B&B which sits next to the
OL,8,Fcastle ruins and says the area's
OL,9,Fhistory is a huge draw for tourists.
OL,11,F"I think the best part about it is
OL,12,Fbeing able to share it, because nobody
OL,13,Fknows we're here," he said.
OL,15,F"Even people who've lived all their
OL,16,Flife in Berwick have never been down
OL,17,Fhere (around the castle.)"
