OL,3,CSiege and slaughter: The border town
OL,4,Cwith a bloody role in British history
OL,6,F"Italian engineers were brought across
OL,7,Fthe help to supervise this 'Star Wars
OL,8,FTechnology' to keep Berwick in English
OL,9,Fhands.
OL,11,F"It was the only town in England that
OL,12,Fhad a set of walls like this built
OL,13,Faround it during this period and shows
OL,14,Fhow important it was strategically.
OL,16,F"It shows why so much money was spent
OL,17,Fhere. It was the most expensive
OL,18,Fproject in the whole of Elizabeth I
OL,19,Freign was building the town's walls. "
