OL,6,FJohn Sadler, part of the reenactment
OL,7,Fgroup the Time Bandits, told ITV Tyne
OL,8,FTees: "Stones almost resonate with the
OL,9,Fhistory and it's almost like an actor
OL,10,Fhaving a set - if you're on a stage
OL,11,Fperfectly adapted to the role you're
OL,12,Ftrying to deliver then history has
OL,13,Fcreated a fantastic stage for us here.
OL,14,FIt's superb.
